{"tid":363551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[青春已逝]覺唔覺依家既人做任何野都少左團火","createTime":"2017-08-17T17:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T09:55:45.000Z","uid":17888,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5929d82d2e713ef60a2dfcbf9d222c8c18737366","tid":363551,"uid":17888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T17:04:15.000Z","msg":"返工等放工<br />\n做野hea 99 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔做錯就得<br />\n日日得過且過<br />\n完全唔追求進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成世人既目標就係買樓<br />\n中左六合彩做啲乜呀<br />\n買多幾層等收租<br />\n唔洗做就有錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我記得以前睇過一個節目<br />\n係講王維基發蹟史<br />\n當年佢岩岩城市電訊搵到錢<br />\n佢第一時間做既，唔係買新樓換大屋<br />\n而將第一桶金放返係公司再碌大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾年我見過最有火既名人一定係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解呀？因為佢夠膽將佢本身有既錢<br />\n拎出黎搞HKTV，唔好理佢依家算唔算成功<br />\n最起碼佢都做過，博過<br />\n衰左一次都仲夠膽企返起身呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知香港仲有幾多個有呢團火，有既，我希望大家堅持住，就算仲有幾細都好，唔好俾佢息左，總有一日，一個機會，團火仲會再次發光發亮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c02e2be80ec7b04434c6359fa4b3b976e02dde9","tid":363551,"uid":34092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T17:10:40.000Z","msg":"同感"},{"pid":"44b0275e347f66b7108d357ad45b66efb8b43b4d","tid":363551,"uid":17888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T17:59:50.000Z","msg":"推俾大家睇"},{"pid":"0d54e97bec4475be3ab4101e46ec5b9bace35980","tid":363551,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:01:32.000Z","msg":"Wiki 真係香港精神"},{"pid":"1ff3701721ffaf920f328a5c25c25665f566b74e","tid":363551,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:01:45.000Z","msg":"大家都係求穩陣<br />\n狀元一定讀醫<br />\n無人會同你博 因為時代唔同左 機會冇以前咁多"},{"pid":"f1d794dcfad71f1ddbccfeadb9ff586a4d772f35","tid":363551,"uid":17888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:10:21.000Z","msg":"推多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a270a739ec21ad513957458388661ea4b0a11af6","tid":363551,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:11:34.000Z","msg":"冇得上位發達，點解要做咁盡？"},{"pid":"4f83c95674ca5055bd00285430e2cc5cce17dbc3","tid":363551,"uid":17888,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇得上位發達，點解要做咁盡？</blockquote><br />\n你係咁灰既話，上位發達果個一定唔會係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a047bd8c533886eb1ee3c3983532e059c3224ca","tid":363551,"uid":17888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39e3d81890a468ec61112b37e8c206088f0355ba","tid":363551,"uid":17888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T08:37:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e841c75ea2c64f6c64c83ea1a082c24becb71b","tid":363551,"uid":17888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T08:37:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"071a63ea91d336c0ed2e275390e3480bbaa8f979","tid":363551,"uid":54574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T08:43:43.000Z","msg":"王維基當年買左樓既話依家就唔會咁折墜"},{"pid":"44965334d67356dd0340e3abd26760698e6af92a","tid":363551,"uid":17888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T09:47:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>王維基當年買左樓既話依家就唔會咁折墜</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有幾折墮"},{"pid":"5bc779edcc7c402f24c9a4004dcc45b0a9ec08f9","tid":363551,"uid":133750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T09:49:07.000Z","msg":"香港咁樣,點樣有火<br />